
[InterrogationFacility X2FacilityTemplate]
DisplayName="Interrogation Facility"
CompletedSummary="Incorporating some of the old methods used by XCOM during the invasion, we can interrogate any captives we have in out brig for intel, and possibly a lead on an ADVENT facility. We can also try our luck at attempting to 'Recruit' said captives, although not all are going to be willing to join is initially."
Summary="This Interrogation Facility allows us to interrogate (Or possibly recruit) captives in our brig, giving us intel, and possibly, a facility lead."

